  "title": "Preschool Chinese Teacher",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong></em></p><ul><li>Plan, supervise and deliver the program in accordance with the policies, guidelines and frameworks</li><li>Prepare and implement the programs and age-appropriate teaching aids.</li><li>Keep accurate records of children’s progress and address the children's educational and developmental needs individually.</li><li>Complete the progress reports of the children for each semester and prepare a developmental portfolio for every child.</li><li>Communicate with parents via the Connection Book at least once a week, weekly team newsletters and conferences.</li><li>Meet the parents to address any concerns.</li><li>Use positive discipline techniques at all times.</li><li>Guide and supervise the Assistant Teacher in the classroom.</li><li>Render basic first aid as and when necessary.</li><li>Responsible for the upkeep of teaching resources, arrangement, appearance, decorations, and learning environment of the classroom.</li><li>Be familiar with all working curriculum documents, handbooks and policy manuals.</li></ul><p><em><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></em></p><ol><li>Diploma in Early Childhood Care & Education</li><li>Creative and inspiring with loving energy</li><li>Excellent communication and classroom management skills</li><li>Knowledge in educational developmen</li></ol><p></p><p>JOBS IN RECRUITMENT CONSULTANCY PTE LTD 19C9565</p><p>VICTORIA KANG YOUFANG R1441743</p>",
